{"title":"How to Search Anime in oxyanime.to? ","content":"<b>Desktop </b>\n<ol>\n<li>Use the search bar on top of OxyAnime page to search anime name. </li>\n<li>Click the A-Z list next to search bar to search anime by alphabet.</li>\n<li>Click the Explore icon next to search bar to search anime by genre or by date. </li>\n<li>Click the Random icon next to search bar to try your luck for random anime. </li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<b>Mobile</b>\n<ol>\n<li>Tap the blue dot on lower right corner, then use the search bar to search anime name. </li>\n<li>Tap the blue dot on lower right corner, then use the A-Z list below search bar to search anime by alphabet. </li>\n<li>Tap the blue dot on lower right corner, then tap the Explore icon below search bar to search anime by genre or by date. </li>\n<li>Tap the blue dot on lower right corner, then tap the Random icon below search bar to try your luck for random anime. </li>\n</ol>\n"}